  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your instinct for self-preservation gives you many advantages.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Cautious Fighter, base attack bonus +3, halfling.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While fighting defensively or taking the total defense action, you gain a bonus on your Reflex saving throws and to your CMD equal to 1/2 of the dodge bonus to AC you gained from taking that action.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When fighting defensively or taking the total defense action, if you attempt a Reflex saving throw or are the target of a combat maneuver, you can spend a number of stamina points up to your Dexterity bonus to gain a bonus on the Reflex save or to your CMD equal to the number of stamina points you spent.",
